body: Hello! I am a Gold JG main looking for a team to play clash with. My champ pool is thicc, and I believe I have a pretty firm grasp of the current meta. Ultimately, my goal is to have fun. That said, I will still be trying my best to win. Who doesn't like free shit? Add me in game on 'Aberrant' if you need yourself a gold jungler and lets chat.
